<section sectnbr = "5A">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B5106043" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Direct Clutch Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106037">A/T Assembly Disassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106064">A/T Assembly Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106041">Direct Clutch Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106042">Direct Clutch Assembly Preliminary Check</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106043001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove plate snap ring (1) then remove direct clutch retaining plate, discs and separator plates.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V10A510073.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.523mm" ver = "01" gw = "184" gh = "109"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tool and hydraulic press, compress direct clutch return spring subassembly, and remove shaft snap ring (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A019">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09926-98310">
09926–98310
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Do not press in direct clutch return spring subassembly more than 0.7 mm (0.03 in.).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Excessive compression may cause damage to direct clutch return spring subassembly and/or piston.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove direct clutch return spring subassembly (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510163.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.656mm" ver = "01" gw = "140" gh = "118"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using finger to block an oil hole (1), apply compressed air (400 – 800 kPa, 4.1 – 8.2 kgf/cm<sup>2</sup>, 58.0 – 116 psi) to opposite oil hole, to assist removal of clutch piston.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510164.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.317mm" ver = "01" gw = "183" gh = "117"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove outer O-ring (1) from direct clutch piston (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510165.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "38.597mm" ver = "01" gw = "184" gh = "92"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove inner O-ring (2) from input shaft subassembly (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510166.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.630mm" ver = "01" gw = "174" gh = "121"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove input shaft seal rings (1) from input shaft subassembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510167.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "42.914mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "105"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106043002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106044">Direct Clutch Assembly Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse disassembly procedure noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Use new seal rings and O-rings. Apply ATF before installation.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Use new shaft snap ring.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not damage direct clutch return spring subassembly (1) and piston by pressing in direct clutch return spring subassembly passing through its original installing position over 0.7 mm (0.03 in.).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5A020">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09926-98310">
09926–98310
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510168.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.063mm" ver = "01" gw = "128" gh = "116"/>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Apply ATF to direct clutch separator plates (4), discs (3) and retaining plate (2).
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Before assembling discs, soak them in ATF for at least two hours.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Install direct clutch separator plates, discs, retaining plate and new plate snap ring (1) to input shaft subassembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510169.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.730mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "124"/>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Install new plate snap ring so that its both ends would be positioned in correct location as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510170.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "95.196mm" ver = "01" gw = "177" gh = "253"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.827in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.861in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Correct
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Incorrect
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Measure direct clutch piston stroke. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106042"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
When piston stroke is out of specification, select direct clutch retaining plate with suitable thickness from among the following table and replace it.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Available direct clutch retaining plate thickness
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.736in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.736in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Thickness
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Identification mark
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
3.0 mm (0.118 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
1
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
3.2 mm (0.126 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
2
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
3.4 mm (0.134 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
3
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
2.8 mm (0.110 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
4
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
